title: Zsolt Müller
text: Zsolt Müller (born 8 April 1984 in <a href="Ny%C3%ADregyh%C3%A1za">Nyíregyháza</a>) is a <a href="Hungarian%20people">Hungarian</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who currently plays for <a href="Ny%C3%ADregyh%C3%A1za%20Spartacus">Nyíregyháza Spartacus</a>.
